### Routes wired in example/events.go:
###   HTTP-1  ByType("http.command")                                       → publishes to Pub/Sub topic
###   HTTP-2  ByType("http.command.webhook") AND JMESPath(name ∈ {webhook,pepe}) → publishes to webhook
###   PS-1    ByType("http.command.result")                                → publishes to webhook
###   PS-2    ByType("com.example.person.created"|".updated")              → publishes to Pub/Sub topic
###
### Round trip "HTTP → Pub/Sub → webhook" = HTTP-1 + PS-1.

### ─── HTTP-1 · binary CE — round trip HTTP → Pub/Sub → webhook ────────
POST http://localhost:8880/command
Content-Type: application/json
Ce-Id: http1-bin-001
Ce-Specversion: 1.0
Ce-Type: http.command
Ce-Source: //test/http-client

{
  "name": "via-pubsub-to-webhook",
  "age": 25
}

### ─── HTTP-1 · structured CE — same round trip ────────────────────────
POST http://localhost:8880/command
Content-Type: application/cloudevents+json

{
  "specversion": "1.0",
  "id": "http1-struct-0000009",
  "type": "http.command",
  "source": "//test/http-client",
  "datacontenttype": "application/json",
  "data": {
    "name": "structured-via-pubsub",
    "age": 91
  }
}

### ─── HTTP-2 · binary CE — direct to webhook (JMESPath match: webhook) ─
POST http://localhost:8880/command
Content-Type: application/json
Ce-Id: http2-bin-webhook
Ce-Specversion: 1.0
Ce-Type: http.command.webhook
Ce-Source: //test/http-client

{
  "name": "webhook",
  "age": 28
}

### ─── HTTP-2 · binary CE — direct to webhook (JMESPath match: pepe) ───
POST http://localhost:8880/command
Content-Type: application/json
Ce-Id: http2-bin-pepe
Ce-Specversion: 1.0
Ce-Type: http.command.webhook
Ce-Source: //test/http-client

{
  "name": "pepe",
  "age": 33
}

### ─── HTTP-2 · structured CE — JMESPath REJECTS (name ∉ allowlist) ────
### Expected: 400, "no matching route" (CE type matches but JMESPath fails).
POST http://localhost:8880/command
Content-Type: application/cloudevents+json

{
  "specversion": "1.0",
  "id": "http2-struct-reject",
  "type": "http.command.webhook",
  "source": "//test/http-client",
  "datacontenttype": "application/json",
  "data": {
    "name": "stranger",
    "age": 40
  }
}

### ─── Preflight validation — payload missing required field "age" ─────
### Expected: 400, validation failed (preflight middleware blocks before handler).
POST http://localhost:8880/command
Content-Type: application/json
Ce-Id: validate-fail-001
Ce-Specversion: 1.0
Ce-Type: http.command
Ce-Source: //test/http-client

{
  "name": "missing-age"
}

### ─── Fallback — plain HTTP, no CE headers ────────────────────────────
### Subscriber assigns type "com.example.http.command". No route covers it.
### Expected: 400, "no matching route".
POST http://localhost:8880/command
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "no-headers",
  "age": 21
}

### ─── Health endpoints (no auth) ──────────────────────────────────────
GET http://localhost:8880/status

###
GET http://localhost:8880/live

###
GET http://localhost:8880/ready
